dcterms:creator: B. Lia
M. Anthimopoulos
dcterms:description: The datasets were from a pilot prospective randomized controlled crossover study of GoCARB, involving 20 adults with Type 1 Diabetes. The CGM measurements were taken every 5 minutes, resulting in 26 sub-datasets with a minimum length of 1500 measurements.
dcterms:title: Datasets from real patients

dcterms:creator: M. Anthimopoulos
dcterms:description: The FDA-accepted UVa/Padova T1D Simulator was used to conduct in silico clinical trials for 11 virtual adult subjects, generating glucose measurements for training and testing the prediction model.
dcterms:title: FDA-accepted UVa/Padova T1D Simulator
